**Killing** | Ability Type
__Basics__
Killing is different from attacking, as it cannot be stopped by most defenses.
__Details__
Killing often happens passively and is then only described as 'dying'.
Most defenses (see `$i defenses`) do not affect kills, but a few do.
Most roles with the ability to kill are considered _Killing_ roles.

__Simplified__
Killing is different from attacking, as it cannot be stopped by most defenses.
Most roles with the ability to kill are considered _Killing_ roles.
